{"tid":353861,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"Sales全部都係咁嘅？","createTime":"2017-08-10T03:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T07:33:54.000Z","uid":56837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"747e967bb75fca25d79350b6dd8560f9db29d921","tid":353861,"uid":56837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:16:32.000Z","msg":"最近番新工，同sales department同一個office<br />\n可能我個部門比較摺，而做野嘅時候都需要幾集中，所以大家唔係太多野講同埋希望環保靜一啲<br />\n但係隔離嘅sales department日日都好似開party咁，無論係其他departmemt內線打比佢地定同緊客傾生意，佢地都係勁high同勁大聲咁講電話<br />\n另外啲女仲日日濃妝濃香水講電話chok晒聲，你話廿幾三十個啲都算啦，四十幾歲個啲竟然仲倡狂過佢地，仲要係背後講壞人話，你估自己仲十八廿二咩，十八加廿二都唔止啦大佬<br />\n<br />\n以前唔係同sales一個office真係唔清楚，其實係咪全部sales都係咁？"},{"pid":"fea2a5d298e95117de3babb975dbe8402b782d7d","tid":353861,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:19:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2724cb53edeac45821627b13a4df846bfa45d145","tid":353861,"uid":56837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:21:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你應該將sales改為女人<br />\n女人全部都係咁嘅？</blockquote><br />\n但係最嘈個啲好似都係男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1575b5e7fd3142087d33c2cab3b49c6dcb59896","tid":353861,"uid":86612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:20:52.000Z","msg":"Sales 唔同客吹水 你摺得la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 毒拎做sales 真係好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956207c477a80215699517653f1bcc5ea9be8b7e","tid":353861,"uid":56837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:46:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sales 唔同客吹水 你摺得la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 毒拎做sales 真係好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傾還傾唔洗扯開個喉嚨姐<br />\n加上佢地同同事傾計多，都係要大叫"},{"pid":"7f4c33b7adf3dc443ad7c6782b1454c2ab50b2d8","tid":353861,"uid":74145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Sales 唔同客吹水 你摺得la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 毒拎做sales 真係好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傾還傾唔洗扯開個喉嚨姐<br />\n加上佢地同同事傾計多，都係要大叫</blockquote><br />\n唔計講壞話呢part其實個風氣幾有趣呀"},{"pid":"1d6e152a8d75a333d1e543a082ed070200d288f6","tid":353861,"uid":56837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Sales 唔同客吹水 你摺得la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 毒拎做sales 真係好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傾還傾唔洗扯開個喉嚨姐<br />\n加上佢地同同事傾計多，都係要大叫</blockquote><br />\n唔計講壞話呢part其實個風氣幾有趣呀</blockquote><br />\n但係我做proofread嘅時候好騷擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}